descriptionHtml:
Update: Have added a lvl 1 save 

has 40k gold, maxed (or close to maxed) a few skills (mostly physical talents), has completed main story, completed stormcloaks\' story, completed thieves guild story, completed dark brotherhood story, completed forsworn story, completed mage\'s tower story, and maybe a few other story lines. I believe i have achieved the title \"Thane\" for most of the holds and have a house in each of them. Currently am not a vampire or werewolf however i do have hercine\'s ring if you wanna be a werewolf. 

This is a list of mods i used to give this character her fine looks.
